 version. It can also auto-enable if the user\'s device is set to Dark Mode or has a low battery, helping save energy.'=>'黑暗模式为网站增加了一个开关，允许用户切换到黑暗版本。如果用户的设备设置为黑暗模式或电池电量不足，它还可以自动启用，帮助节省能源。','Switch Button Type'=>'开关按钮类型','Select type of your dark mode switch button.'=>'选择黑暗模式开关按钮的类型。','Select Switch Button Type'=>'选择开关按钮类型','Menu Switch'=>'菜单开关','Floating Button'=>'浮动按钮','OS Aware Dark Mode'=>'操作系统感知黑暗模式','OS aware dark mode automatically switches your website to a dark mode if your user\'s device OS theme preference is set to Dark in display settings.'=>'如果用户的设备操作系统主题偏好在显示设置中设置为暗色，操作系统感知暗色模式会自动将网站切换为暗色模式。','Auto-enable Dark Mode if the user\'s device is set to Dark Mode.'=>'如果用户的设备已设置为暗色模式，则自动启用暗色模式。','Battery Low Dark Mode'=>'电池电量低黑暗模式','Battery low dark mode automatically switches your website to a dark mode if your user\'s device battery level is less than 10%, thus saving their battery from draining fast.'=>'如果用户的设备电池电量低于 10%，电池电量低黑暗模式会自动将网站切换为黑暗模式，从而避免电池快速耗尽。','Auto-enable Dark Mode if your user\'s device battery level is low.'=>'如果用户的设备电池电量不足，可自动启用黑暗模式。','Select on what device types dark mode feature should be active and running.'=>'选择暗模式功能应在哪些设备类型上激活和运行。','Pull Down Refresh'=>'下拉刷新','Pull down refresh touchscreen gesture allows your users to drag the screen and then release it, as a signal to the application to refresh contents of your web app.'=>'下拉刷新触摸屏手势允许用户拖动屏幕，然后松开，以此向应用程序发出信号，刷新网络应用程序的内容。','Select on what device types pull down navigation feature should be active and running.'=>'选择下拉导航功能应在哪些设备上激活和运行。','Shake Refresh'=>'奶昔刷新','Shake refresh gesture brings amazing UX experience to your users by simply shaking phone as a signal to your web application to refresh the contents of the screen.'=>'摇动刷新手势可为用户带来令人惊叹的用户体验，只需摇动手机，网络应用程序就会发出信号，刷新屏幕内容。','Select on what device types swipe navigation feature should be active and running.'=>'选择哪些设备类型应激活和运行轻扫导航功能。','Page Loader'=>'页面加载器','Page Loader feature gives you ability to show a nice page loader animation between page loadings. Page Loader appears at the start of page load and disappears after it is fully loaded.'=>'页面加载器功能可在页面加载之间显示漂亮的页面加载器动画。页面加载器在页面加载开始时出现，并在页面完全加载后消失。','Page Loader Type'=>'页面加载器类型','Select the type of page loader you want on your website.'=>'选择您希望在网站上使用的页面加载器类型。','Select Page Loader Type'=>'选择页面加载器类型','Your PWA icon (your website logo) bounces in the middle of the screen, providing a simple and recognizable loading animation.'=>'您的 PWA 图标（您的网站徽标）会在屏幕中间跳动，提供一个简单易识别的加载动画。','Default'=>'默认值','Shows a skeleton loading screen, providing a placeholder layout that mimics the structure of the content being loaded, enhancing perceived performance.'=>'显示骨架加载屏幕，提供模仿加载内容结构的占位符布局，提高感知性能。','Skeleton'=>'骨架','Displays spinning circles as the loading animation, indicating that the page is loading with a familiar, straightforward visual.'=>'将旋转的圆圈显示为加载动画，以熟悉、直观的视觉效果表示页面正在加载。','Spinner'=>'旋转器','Features a flying man icon moving across a yellow background, offering a fun and playful loading experience that entertains users while they wait.'=>'黄色背景上有一个飞人图标在移动，提供了一种有趣的加载体验，让用户在等待时也能得到娱乐。','Redirect'=>'重定向','Displays the loading percentage and a progress bar, giving users a clear and precise indication of the page loading progress.'=>'显示加载百分比和进度条，让用户清晰准确地了解页面加载进度。','Smooth transition with fade in and fade out effects, creating a seamless and visually appealing loading experience.'=>'通过淡入和淡出效果实现平滑过渡，创造出无缝和具有视觉吸引力的加载体验。','Select on what device types page loader feature should be active and running.'=>'选择页面加载器功能应在哪些设备类型上激活和运行。','Inactive Blur'=>'非活动模糊','Inactive Blur feature blurs the website when it\'s not focused, so when the user switches to another tab in browser or will minimize your website as a background task your website will be blurred.'=>'非活动模糊功能会在网站未聚焦时使其模糊，因此当用户切换到浏览器的另一个标签页或将网站最小化为背景任务时，网站就会模糊。','Select on what device types inactive blur feature should be active and running.'=>'选择哪些设备类型的非活动模糊功能应处于活动和运行状态。','Toast Messages'=>'祝酒词','Toast messages provide simple feedback about an operation in a small popup. It only fills the amount of space required for the message and the current activity remains visible and interactive. Toasts automatically disappear after a timeout.'=>'祝酒词通过一个小弹出窗口提供有关操作的简单反馈。它只占用信息所需的空间，而当前活动仍然可见并具有交互性。敬酒信息会在超时后自动消失。','Select on what device types toast messages feature should be active and running.'=>'选择哪些设备类型的吐司信息功能应激活并运行。','App Identity'=>'应用程序身份','Define the core identifiers of your app such as the name, short name, icon, description, and categories which represent your app across devices and platforms.'=>'定义应用程序的核心标识符，如名称、简称、图标、描述和类别，以便在各种设备和平台上代表应用程序。','App Icon'=>'应用程序图标','Upload an icon representing your app, used for home screen and app listings. Ideally your web app icon should be the logo of your website.'=>'上传一个代表你的应用程序的图标，用于主屏幕和应用程序列表。理想情况下，您的网络应用程序图标应该是您网站的徽标。','Select Icon'=>'选择图标','Minimum 100x100 PNG, JPG, JPEG, or WEBP image.'=>'最小尺寸为 100x100 的 PNG、JPG、JPEG 或 WEBP 图像。','App Screenshots'=>'应用程序截图','Upload screenshots of your app to showcase its features and user interface in app stores. By default, we auto-generate one mobile and one desktop version screenshot of your homepage, but you can add up to 5 screenshots of different screens and sizes.'=>'上传应用程序的屏幕截图，以便在应用程序商店中展示其功能和用户界面。默认情况下，我们会自动生成一张移动版和一张桌面版的主页截图，但您最多可以添加 5 张不同屏幕和尺寸的截图。','Drop your screenshots here or'=>'请在此处或','browse'=>'浏览','Select up to 5 screenshots.'=>'最多选择 5 张截图。','App Name'=>'应用程序名称','Specify the full name of your web application, typically matching your business or service name.'=>'指定网络应用程序的全名，通常与业务或服务名称相匹配。','Enter App Name'=>'输入应用程序名称','Short Name'=>'简称','Provide a brief version (up to 12 characters) of your app’s name for display on home screens and dashboards.'=>'提供应用程序名称的简短版本（最多 12 个字符），以便在主屏幕和仪表板上显示。','Enter Short Name'=>'输入简称','Description'=>'说明','Enter a concise summary of your app\'s purpose and main features.'=>'输入应用目的和主要功能的简明摘要。','Enter Description'=>'输入描述','Categories'=>'类别','The categories describe the expected application categories to which the web application belongs. It\'s used as a hint to catalogs or store listing web applications. We recommend not to choose more than 3 categories.'=>'类别描述了网络应用所属的预期应用类别。它可作为目录或商店列出网络应用程序的提示。我们建议选择的类别不要超过 3 个。','Select Categories'=>'选择类别','Books'=>'书籍','Business'=>'商业','Education'=>'教育','Entertainment'=>'娱乐','Finance'=>'财务','Fitness'=>'健身','Food'=>'食品','Games'=>'游戏','Government'=>'政府','Health'=>'健康','Kids'=>'儿童','Lifestyle'=>'生活方式','Magazines'=>'杂志','Medical'=>'医疗','News'=>'新闻','Personalization'=>'个性化','Photo'=>'照片','Politics'=>'政治','Productivity'=>'生产率','Security'=>'安全','Shopping'=>'购物','Social'=>'社会','Sports'=>'体育','Travel'=>'旅行','Utilities'=>'公用设施','Weather'=>'天气','Display Settings'=>'显示屏设置','Customize how your app appears and behaves on user screens, including the startup page, display layout, and screen orientation.'=>'自定义应用程序在用户屏幕上的显示和行为方式，包括启动页面、显示布局和屏幕方向。','Start Page'=>'起始页','Set the initial page that loads when your app is launched from the home screen. In normal cases it should be your homepage.'=>'设置从主屏幕启动应用程序时加载的初始页面。一般情况下，这应该是您的主页。','Select Start Page'=>'选择起始页','Display Mode'=>'显示模式','Choose how your app displays. We recommend choosing "Standalone", as it provides a native app feeling.'=>'选择应用程序的显示方式。我们建议选择 "独立"，因为它能给人一种原生应用的感觉。','Select Display Mode'=>'选择显示模式','Opens the app in a separate window for a native app experience.'=>'在单独窗口中打开应用程序，体验原生应用程序。','Standalone'=>'单机版','Expands the app to cover the entire screen, hiding browser UI.'=>'将应用程序扩展至覆盖整个屏幕，隐藏浏览器用户界面。','Fullscreen'=>'全屏','Displays the app with minimal browser UI for a cleaner interface.'=>'以最小的浏览器用户界面显示应用程序，使界面更简洁。','Minimal UI'=>'极简用户界面','Orientation'=>'定向','Select the preferred screen orientation. We recommend choosing "Portrait", as it provides a more native app feeling.'=>'选择首选的屏幕方向。我们建议选择 "纵向"，因为它提供了一种更原生的应用程序感觉。','Select Orientation'=>'选择方向','Allow Both'=>'同时允许','Portrait'=>'肖像','Landscape'=>'景观','Appearance'=>'外观','Adjust the visual elements of your app, including the theme and background colors, to enhance the user interface and align with your branding.'=>'调整应用程序的视觉元素，包括主题和背景颜色，以增强用户界面并与品牌形象保持一致。','iOS Status Bar Style'=>'iOS 状态栏风格','Specify the style of the status bar for your app on iOS devices.'=>'指定 iOS 设备上应用程序状态栏的样式。','Select iOS Status Bar Style'=>'选择 iOS 状态栏样式','White bar with black text'=>'白色条形图配黑色文字','Black bar with white text'=>'黑条白字','Transparent bar with white text'=>'带白色文字的透明条','Theme Color'=>'主题颜色','Define the primary color theme for the browser\'s toolbar and app\'s header. It should be the same as the main color palette of your website.'=>'定义浏览器工具栏和应用程序标题的主色调。它应与网站的主色调相同。','Background Color'=>'背景颜色','Choose a background color that displays during app startup and loading. It should be the same as the background color of your website.'=>'选择一种在应用程序启动和加载时显示的背景颜色。背景颜色应与网站的背景颜色相同。','Advanced Features'=>'高级功能','Expand your app’s functionality with advanced features like age ratings, related applications, and customizable shortcuts to various app functions.'=>'利用年龄分级、相关应用程序和自定义各种应用程序功能快捷方式等高级功能扩展应用程序的功能。','IARC Rating ID'=>'国际癌症研究机构评级 ID','International Age Rating Coalition (IARC) certification number, which helps classify your app’s appropriate age group. Click the info icon for more information.'=>'国际年龄分级联盟 (IARC) 认证编号，有助于将您的应用程序划分为相应的年龄组。点击信息图标了解更多信息。','Enter IARC Rating ID'=>'输入 IARC 评级 ID','Related Applications'=>'相关应用','Related application option gives you the ability to list your native applications related to your web app, for cross-promotion or additional functionality. So if you will relate your native application to your PWA, the browser will prompt the user with your native app instead of the PWA web app. If you don\'t have a native application for your web app, you can request them by clicking the "Publish to App Stores" button on the header or navigation menu.'=>'相关应用程序选项可让您列出与网络应用程序相关的本地应用程序，以进行交叉推广或实现附加功能。因此，如果您将本地应用程序与 PWA 相关联，浏览器就会提示用户使用本地应用程序，而不是 PWA 网络应用程序。如果您的网络应用程序没有本地应用程序，您可以点击标题或导航菜单上的 "发布到应用程序商店 "按钮来申请本地应用程序。','Don\'t have native apps? Get them and %1$spublish to app stores%2$s'=>'没有本地应用程序？获取它们并%1$s发布到应用程序商店%2$s','Select Platform'=>'选择平台','iOS'=>'iOS','Enter App ID'=>'输入应用程序 ID','Add Related Application'=>'添加相关应用程序','App Shortcuts'=>'应用程序快捷方式','App shortcuts help users quickly start common or recommended tasks within your web app. Easy access to those tasks from anywhere the app icon is displayed will enhance users productivity as well as increase their engagement with the web app. The app shortcuts menu is invoked by right-clicking the app icon in the taskbar (Windows) or dock (macOS) on the user\'s desktop, or long pressing the app\'s launcher icon on Android.'=>'应用程序快捷方式可帮助用户在网络应用程序中快速启动常用任务或推荐任务。在显示应用程序图标的任何位置都能轻松访问这些任务，这将提高用户的工作效率，并增加他们对网络应用程序的参与度。右键单击用户桌面任务栏（Windows）或 dock（macOS）上的应用图标，或长按安卓系统上的应用启动器图标，即可调用应用快捷方式菜单。','Enter Shortcut Name'=>'输入快捷方式名称','Select Shortcut Page'=>'选择快捷页面','Add App Shortcut'=>'添加应用程序快捷方式','v%s'=>'v%s','Auto (system default)'=>'自动（系统默认）','Light'=>'灯光','Dark'=>'黑暗','Help Centre'=>'帮助中心','What\'s New'=>'最新消息','Progressify'=>'进步','You\'re Offline'=>'您已离线','It looks like you lost your internet connection. Please check your connection to reconnect.'=>'您好像失去了网络连接。请检查您的连接以重新连接。','Reconnect'=>'重新连接','Publish your web app to stores'=>'向商店发布网络应用程序','Enable secure HTTPS on your server'=>'在服务器上启用安全 HTTPS','It appears you do not have a secure HTTPS server and PWA requires HTTPS connection to function correctly. Please set up it on your server or contact to your hosting provider to enable it for you.'=>'看来您没有安全的 HTTPS 服务器，而 PWA 需要 HTTPS 连接才能正常运行。请在您的服务器上进行设置，或联系您的托管提供商为您启用。','Upload or select your PWA App Icon'=>'上传或选择您的 PWA 应用程序图标','Define your PWA web app Name'=>'定义 PWA 网络应用程序名称','Define your PWA web app Short Name'=>'定义 PWA 网络应用程序的简称','Choose your PWA web app categories'=>'选择您的 PWA 网络应用程序类别','Enable PWA Installation Prompts'=>'启用 PWA 安装提示','Enable one of the PWA Installation Overlays'=>'启用其中一个 PWA 安装覆盖层','Enable Offline Cache for your PWA'=>'为您的 PWA 启用离线缓存','Enable Advanced Web Capabilities for your PWA'=>'为您的 PWA 启用高级网络功能','Enable the Background Sync feature'=>'启用后台同步功能','Enable the Periodic Background Sync feature'=>'启用定期后台同步功能','Enable Push Notifications Prompt or Button'=>'启用推送通知提示或按钮','The notification was sent to %d out of %d recipients, with %d failure.'=>'通知已发送给 %d 个收件人中的 %d，失败 %d。','Sending failed. There was an error on server.'=>'发送失败。服务器出错。','New %s - %s'=>'新 %s - %s','Price Drop - %s'=>'降价 - %s','Price dropped from %s to %s'=>'价格从 %s 降至 %s','New Sale Price - %s'=>'新售价 - %s','New Sale Price: %s'=>'新售价: %s','Back In Stock - %s'=>'返回库存 - %s','%s is now back in stock'=>'%s 现已恢复库存','Your Order Status Updated'=>'您的订单状态已更新','Your order (ID %s) status has updated from %s to %s. Click on this notification to see the order.'=>'您的订单（ID %s）状态已从 %s 更新为 %s。点击此通知查看订单。','New Comment By %s'=>'新评论 %s','New Order #%s'=>'新秩序 #%s','New order from %s for %s%s (%d items)'=>'来自 %s 的 %s%s 新订单（%d 个项目）','Low Stock Alert: %s'=>'低库存警报：%s','Stock level: %d (Threshold: %d)%s. SKU: %s'=>'库存水平：%d（阈值：%d）%s。SKU：%s','%s has just mentioned you in a %s'=>'%s 刚刚在 %s 中提到了您','New mention from %s'=>'来自 %s 的新提法','New comment from %s'=>'来自 %s 的新评论','%s has just commented on your post.'=>'%s 刚刚评论了您的帖子。','New reply from %s'=>'来自 %s 的新回复','%s has just replied to you.'=>'%s 刚刚回复了您。','New message from %s'=>'来自 %s 的新消息','New friend request from %s'=>'来自 %s 的新好友请求','%s has just sent you a friend request.'=>'%s 刚刚向您发送了好友请求。','Friend request accepted'=>'接受好友请求','%s has just accepted your friend request.'=>'%s 刚刚接受了您的好友请求。','⚠️ %s requires PHP version at least 8.2 to function properly.'=>'⚠️ %s 需要至少 8.2 的 PHP 版本才能正常运行。','If you have trouble fixing this, please contact us on'=>'如果您在修复时遇到困难，请通过以下方式联系我们','⚠️ %s features require <i>%s</i> extension to function properly.'=>'⚠️ %s 功能需要 <i>%s</i> 扩展才能正常运行。','Notifications are not supported by your browser.'=>'您的浏览器不支持通知功能。','You need to accept the notifications permission to p